PAUL RULE SYSTEM (Cursor)

1.  Purpose
    A.  Point Cursor at the repository's rule system under
        `paul/`.

2.  Prompt handling
    A.  Read and apply `.cursor/rules/prompt.mdc` to each prompt.
    B.  Update `paul/chat_log.txt` for each prompt. Do not
        skip unless the user explicitly asks you not to.
    C.  Maintain spec files in `paul/` (spec_*.txt) when
        prompts change primary app features outside `paul/`.

3.  Rule file formatting
    A.  When editing any file in `paul/`, apply
        `.cursor/rules/outline.mdc`.
